relevant_findings.general: Chronically-ill appearing in no acute distress
relevant_findings.HEENT: NC/AT, PERRLA, EOMI, sclerae anicteric, mucous membranes moist, oropharynx clear
relevant_findings.lungs: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no rales/rhonchi/wheezes, good air movement, respiratory effort unlabored, no accessory muscle use
relevant_findings.heart: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs/rubs/gallops, normal S1-S2
relevant_findings.abdomen: Soft, tender in epigastrium with quiet bowel sounds, no rebound tenderness, no masses or hepatosplenomegaly
relevant_findings.neuro: Awake, alert and oriented x3, cranial nerves II-XII intact, muscle strength appropriate
